window.bookSummaryJSON = "A dedicated and loving mother's worst nightmare comes true when her daughter is stolen from her crib in the middle of the night. After weeks of inquiries, press conferences, and prayers, what comes home may not actually be the girl who was taken after all. \"Gracie Is Gone\" is a short horror tale that can be found in the collection <i>Certain Dark Things</i>, also available on Audible.com."; 
